            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tortilla</strong> to a clean board and using your finger, rub some of the <strong>flour paste </strong>along the edge of one quarter of the tortilla</p><p>Fold the <strong>tortilla</strong> in half and press firmly to seal the bottom half, leaving an opening at the top</p><p>Tip: This will make filling your tortillas easier!</p><p>Repeat this with the remaining tortillas – these are your <strong>tortilla shells</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1678875913403-x200.jpg",
