            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> black bean & sweet potato mix</strong> between the <strong>tortilla shells</strong></p><p>Use the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>flour paste </strong>to seal the top half of the tortilla shells – these are your <strong>plant-based black bean & sweet potato tortilla pockets</strong></p><p>Tip: Press firmly on the edges to make sure there are no gaps!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
