        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>in a large bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> baby leaf salad </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then add it to the <strong>dressing </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
